# Smart URL Shortener

A simple web application that converts long URLs into short, shareable links.

## Features

- Generate short URLs from long links
- Custom short aliases
- Automatic URL correction (adds https:// if missing)
- Click tracking analytics
- Copy-to-clipboard button
- Responsive UI using Bootstrap

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Flask
- SQLite
- Flask-SQLAlchemy
- Bootstrap

